# Installation

## Requirements

You need to install [Guile][1] and its development headers.

```Shell
sudo aptitude install guile-2.0 guile-2.0-dev
```

You can also install the Guile documentation.

```
sudo aptitude install guile-2.0-doc
```

## Installation

You can install AIscm from an archive as follows:

```
wget https://github.com/wedesoft/aiscm/releases/download/v@VERSION@/aiscm-@VERSION@.tar.xz
tar xf aiscm-@VERSION@.tar.xz
cd aiscm-@VERSION@
./configure
make
sudo make install
```

## Testing

After installing AIscm you can run the test suite like this:

```
make check
```

[1]: http://www.gnu.org/software/guile/
